accesses.name: NOVOTEL VERSAILLES LE CHESNAY
accesses.description: From Paris: take exit 6 (Le Chesnay) on A13 then follow Versailles. From Rouen: take exit 6 (Versailles Centre) on A13, then follow Versailles. From the A12: head for Le Chesnay, then Versailles. From Vélizy-Orly: take the Versailles Centre exit on A86, f ollow Château then Saint Germain en Laye/Toutes directions. By train from Paris Saint-Lazare: Versailles Rive Droite stop, then 15 mins walk. From Paris Montparnasse: Versailles Chantier stop, then bus B. By RER C: Versailles Rive Gauche stop, then bus B.
